## Availability filter

This filter searches [booking products](docs.getvoxel.io_articles_booking-product-mode_.md) availability by date or date range. It uses as a source aÂ [Product field](docs.getvoxel.io_articles_product-field_.md)

## Options

- Label
- Key
- Data source: Requires a Product date field as source
- Input mode: Single date or Date range
- Date range matching:

1\. Lazy: Match posts having at least one available day in given range

2\. Greedy: Match posts having every day available in given range
